面攬著她, 雙手會在胸上攬住太太, 有時覺得係親子/係愛, 但見成日都係咁, 我有次就當面半幽默的說, 嘩! 咁大個仔仲咁攬妳媽咪, 丑唔丑, 掂到個胸就係非禮架啦, 佢當堂都唔好意思.<br />\n<br />\n當單獨對我太太時, 我都叫佢避忌下, 青春期對性係好奇, 但我們要幫他們走向正面, 一些越軌的事, 要好小心處理."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T03:53:12.000Z","msg":"高質reply from baby kingdom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2f10ef480e3fd6109e12cb14e8a7dd3f52a246","tid":995874,"uid":16070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T04:01:13.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641d6546a58ad866336ab06a92aa6d7d55a056a1","tid":995874,"uid":131441,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T04:06:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1295b44cd21f4dbed3eb990a63c3d5f790d1ea5","tid":995874,"uid":228269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意咪塞返個女入去囉"},{"pid":"6ab61a2a374c80deeae1196cb7e4a82187d286e9","tid":995874,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T04:12:20.000Z","msg":"做女人做到咁蠢 抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61236ed88d35fb0cdd0001a4d09685f7912e3f4c","tid":995874,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T04:15:58.000Z","msg":"比佢去拍拖啦 即刻無事"},{"pid":"371a0acda043dbf237280ad48030b0549775c575","tid":995874,"uid":45498,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T04:38:08.000Z","msg":"死返去Baby condom 啦 <br />\nC你老母個臭6呀 你講咩呀識唔識中文呀臭雞<br />\n<br />\n個女你生出黎 為人父毋<br />\n生完出黎仇視個女你係咪有撚病呀<br />\n<br />\n你自己死返去娘家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88246305d8ada803e48ad6bf143157c6349f823","tid":995874,"uid":45498,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T04:39:11.000Z","msg":"你心理醫生都話你最好俾人收入青山呀"},{"pid":"37